title: Microsoft Office 2003 Portable - Quick Install - Word, Excel, Po
description:
Here's a sweet little MS office 2003 portable that I've found. Only 70mb in size!

Includes

- Microsoft Word 2003
- Microsoft Excel 2003
- Microsoft Powerpoint 2003
- Microsoft Outlook 2003

Runs much more smoothly than 2007 versions + it's portable and quick install.

Just run the file and it will install automatically on it's own to your c:/program files folder. You can't choose directly with this though so that's a shame - other than that it works perfectly. Enjoy!
